{"tid":405862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前曼聯中堅里奧費迪南轉做職業拳手","createTime":"2017-09-19T07:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T10:47:51.000Z","uid":8968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"035abf3aad0c87408a49d250abcda5b9352d3cce","tid":405862,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/153559_9f8df24546956e08627649b9e82154d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F153559_9f8df24546956e08627649b9e82154d2.jpg&h=5b58a6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n里奧費迪南因愛妻病逝，化身湊仔公帶住3個仔女返學所拍下嘅真人show洋葱專訪，依家睇番都仲咁令人眼濕濕；38歲嘅佢嚟緊又有新搞作，就係好似張家輝套《激戰》咁，幾廿歲人先嚟上擂台，進軍職業拳壇轉做職業拳手，而佢嘅訓練過程將會有全程拍攝，可能又係另一個催淚節目。 <br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，里奧費迪南在曼聯當打時期體重係82公斤，將會挑戰重磅級別賽事，而佢2015年掛靴，估計體重又再增加，若然超過90公斤就要挑戰重量級拳賽，至於詳細情況，佢稍後時間就會開記者會公布。"},{"pid":"0f651a74deec0aff51d11dd7b7925d9453041a86","tid":405862,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"月巴出年無波踢都要打拳"},{"pid":"758f0f78c7376ab6cc41a4ac0cc2fd1e789332af","tid":405862,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月巴出年無波踢都要打拳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月巴做車手"},{"pid":"91012b62f5b96688a4cac7288e4e9f8bd9dfa14e","tid":405862,"uid":125061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"要去熱拳館操操先"},{"pid":"752b2423c9b8e200860e4106e33bf333c510b00d","tid":405862,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c61551532b204c3c806157c5f53ac74cddc3f3","tid":405862,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DKEX0Y0WsAEY3gS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih